title: Kickbacks
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Pizza, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Gastropub offering 180+ beers on tap including seasonal brews. Has vegetarian options that can be made vegan. Choices include coconut bacon bits, beer brats, a beer brat club sandwich, build your own pasta, carrot dogs, and a savory fritter with tzatziki sauce.
